name: PlayStation Underground: Jampack Summer 2002
synopsis: A collection of demos from the Official PlayStation Magazine. The disc contains demos of [[Crash Bandicoot: The Wrath of Cortex]], [[Freekstyle]], [[Frequency]], [[Half-Life]], [[Hot Shots Golf 3]], [[Jak and Daxter: The Precursor Legacy]], [[PaRappa the Rapper 2]], [[Star Wars: Jedi Starfighter]], [[TimeSplitters 2]] as well as videos of [[Kingdom Hearts]] and [[SOCOM: U.S. Navy SEALs]].
